<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Backend {{ inventory_hostname }}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        h1 {
            color: #2c3e50;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #3498db;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .info {
            background-color: #ecf0f1;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .info p {
            margin: 5px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .label {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #34495e;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>üñ•Ô∏è Backend Server: {{ inventory_hostname }}</h1>
        <div class="info">
            <p><span class="label">Hostname:</span> {{ ansible_hostname }}</p>
            <p><span class="label">Private IP:</span> {{ ansible_default_ipv4.address | default('unknown') }}</p>
            <p><span class="label">Public IP:</span> {{ inventory_hostname }}</p>
            <p><span class="label">Server:</span> Apache HTTPD</p>
            <p><span class="label">Status:</span> ‚úÖ Active</p>
        </div>
        <p>This backend server is part of a high-availability cluster behind an Nginx load balancer.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
